@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<h1>About BlazorApp1</h1>

<p>
    BlazorApp1 is a compact demonstration app built with server-hosted Blazor (ASP.NET Core, .NET 8). It showcases interactive server rendering, small data-driven pages and integration with public APIs for learning and experimentation.
</p>

<p>
    It is intended as sample/demo code — features like the Todo list are in-memory and API lookups use public endpoints without authentication.
</p>
